{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.240", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.920", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Thema Hartz-IV-Sanktionen ist ein parlamentarischer Dauerbrenner,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.040", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Die Linke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.640", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute wieder Frau Kipping, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.320", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meistens damit begr\u00fcndet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.520", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie gegen Grundrechte versto\u00dfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.560", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will einige grunds\u00e4tzliche Ausf\u00fchrungen zu dem Thema \u201eGrundrechte und Menschenrechte\u201c machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um unsere Haltung zu pr\u00e4zisieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschenrechte sind vorstaatliche Rechte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.640", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr diese Erkenntnis muss ich kein Vertragstheoretiker sein oder in dieser Tradition stehen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.520", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ergibt sich durch einen Blick in unsere Verfassung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zuerst kommen die Menschenrechte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann die Ausf\u00fchrungen zu den staatlichen Organen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.000", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Staat erh\u00e4lt seine Legitimation durch den Schutz der Menschenrechte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.200", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ich allerdings dar\u00fcber nachdenke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in einem vorstaatlichen Zustand \u00fcberhaupt Rechte begr\u00fcndet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann es nur eine Antwort geben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Tatsache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es Pflichten gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vornehmlich die Pflicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Rechte anderer zu achten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als Voraussetzung daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch meine Rechte geachtet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechte und Pflichten sind also untrennbar miteinander verkn\u00fcpft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aufeinander bezogen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne Pflichten keine Rechte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.480", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Philosoph Otfried H\u00f6ffe spricht in diesem Zusammenhang von einem transzendentalen Tausch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der aus der wechselseitigen Anerkennung der Menschenrechte als rechtsmoralischer Anspruch entsteht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.040", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Reziprozit\u00e4t ist ein Schl\u00fcsselelement dieses Kerns der Menschenrechte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Freilich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Menschenrechte haben noch einen zus\u00e4tzlichen Aspekt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.480", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie gelten auch dort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.480", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo keine Reziprozit\u00e4t geleistet werden kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.160", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir diesen Gedanken weiterf\u00fchren und auf das staatliche Handeln \u00fcbertragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.200", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ergibt sich daraus: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Staat sch\u00fctzt die Rechte der Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sie im vorstaatlichen Zustand haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.440", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar sowohl die, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die durch den rechtsmoralischen Anspruch des Tausches zustande gekommen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.280", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als auch diese, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.600", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei denen wir Reziprozit\u00e4t nicht erwarten k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Konkreter formuliert: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.800", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist eine Person nicht handlungsf\u00e4hig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verliert sie auch nicht ihre Menschenrechte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.120", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei unserer Debatte ist die Lage freilich diese: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Empf\u00e4nger von Hilfen nach SGB\u00a0II ist nach unserem Verst\u00e4ndnis zu Reziprozit\u00e4t in der Lage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.000", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den Anspr\u00fcchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.360", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die er gegen\u00fcber der Gemeinschaft als Rechte geltend machen kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "entsprechen Pflichten aus dem urspr\u00fcnglichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.880", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem rechtsmoralisch begr\u00fcndeten Tauschverh\u00e4ltnis. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.520", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Versto\u00dfe ich gegen diese Pflichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hebe ich selbst den engen Zusammenhang von Rechten und Pflichten auf; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.000", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Pflicht zur Hilfeleistung erlischt aus meiner Sicht durch einen Verzicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.600", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00f6chten Sie eine Zwischenfrage zulassen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.080", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "danke. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde das gerne zu Ende ausf\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.280", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist der Kern der Debatte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir heute f\u00fchren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.520", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kann ich Rechte geltend machen und gleichzeitig die damit einhergehenden Pflichten au\u00dfer Kraft setzen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir meinen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.920", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn damit wird ein Grundprinzip der Menschenrechte im Kern ber\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.560", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich das der geschuldeten Reziprozit\u00e4t dort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.560", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo sie geleistet werden kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den Bezug von Leistungen nach SGB\u00a0II sanktionsfrei zu stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hei\u00dft damit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.000", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein schon naturrechtlich begr\u00fcndetes wechselseitiges Bedingungsverh\u00e4ltnis zugunsten der Rechte zu suspendieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.640", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich f\u00fcrchte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.920", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine solche Forderung nicht nur die Idee der Menschenrechte selbst besch\u00e4digt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.560", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern vor allem die Voraussetzungen gesellschaftlicher Solidarit\u00e4t untergr\u00e4bt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcberdies entspricht ein Menschenbild, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.760", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das nur Rechte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.560", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber keine Pflichten kennt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.840", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht dem meinen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.040", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es w\u00e4re ironischerweise ein Menschenbild, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das in einem beinahe darwinistischen Individualismus endet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.880", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den nicht einmal die Erben des politischen Liberalismus vertreten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.480", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dies aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.160", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.360", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen die Erben der postsozialistischen Tradition mit sich selbst ausmachen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.000", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich erteile das Wort zu einer Kurzintervention dem Kollegen Straetmanns von der Fraktion Die Linke."
   ]
  }
 ]
}